We care about your questions and concerns.
If you are contacting Valeant Pharmaceuticals International, Inc. about a donation request, please note that although we would like to assist all of the many worthy individuals, organizations and causes contacting us with requests, we are unable to help in every instance as our contributions efforts focus on very specific activities. We hope you understand our position, and we wish you all the best with your efforts.
Please note that Valeant Pharmaceuticals International, Inc. does not accept unsolicited requests for funding.
For any other questions that you may have, please use the form below. Typical response time is 2-3 business days, depending on the nature of the question. Please note that we do not respond to form letters or e-mail campaigns.




